				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				I've found this spell is very useful when soloing undead in Ro/Oasis.  First, cast engulfing darkness.  Once in place (unresisted), then cast spook the dead.  Then, lay into it with ward undead (or the equivalent for your level) while pet hits it.  When spook runs out, run from the mob while pet continues hitting it (the mob WILL be very ticked at you).  Using this technique, I've taken on yellow crypt mummies at level 13 without too much trouble.
